OL,3,C'Such little regard for life': Family
OL,4,Ccriticise medics for care failure
OL,6,FIn a statement, Mr Irvine's family
OL,7,Fsays: "We are convinced, as are many
OL,8,Fothers, that if even basic first aid
OL,9,Fhad been administered then Frazer may
OL,10,Fwell have survived.
OL,12,F"The actions of the paramedics fell
OL,13,Fwell below any acceptable standards of
OL,14,Fcare, even the expert hired by the
OL,15,Fdefendants could not defend their
OL,16,Factions.
