OL,3,C'Such little regard for life': Family
OL,4,Ccriticise medics for care failure
OL,6,F"On 18 March 2022, Frazer reached out
OL,7,Ffor help but was tragically let down
OL,8,Fby those whose job it was to
OL,9,Fadminister that help. What is hard to
OL,10,Faccept is that those in a caring
OL,11,Fprofession could show such little
OL,12,Fregard for human life."
OL,14,FThe family adds: "Frazer was a much-
OL,15,Floved son, brother, uncle and friend.
OL,16,FThe efforts to portray Frazer as a
OL,17,Fviolent, aggressive drunk could not be
OL,18,Ffurther from the truth.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
