OL,3,C'Such little regard for life': Family
OL,4,Ccriticise medics for care failure
OL,6,F"Anyone who viewed the CCTV that the
OL,7,Fparamedics obviously never realised
OL,8,Fwas recording, the subsequent evidence
OL,9,Ffrom body worn cameras and the
OL,10,Fevidence provided in court by
OL,11,Fwitnesses will be aware of the truth.
OL,13,F"The authorities in Jersey do not
OL,14,Fbring cases lightly. They must decide
OL,15,Fthat there is both a reasonable
OL,16,Fprospect of conviction and that the
OL,17,Fprosecution is in the public interest."
OL,19,FHowever, Le Sauteur and Sutherland
OL,20,Fhave told ITV News that they intend to
OL,21,Fappeal the decision of Jurats.
