OL,3,C'Such little regard for life': Family
OL,4,Ccriticise medics for care failure
OL,6,FThe two men were sentenced at Jersey's
OL,7,FRoyal Court to pay #500 each in legal
OL,8,Fcosts and issued a 'conditional
OL,9,Fdischarge' for two years - which means
OL,10,Fthey will not face punishment unless
OL,11,Fthey re-offend within two years.
OL,13,FLe Sauteur explains: "We will be
OL,14,Flodging an appeal in the next week or
OL,15,Fso to overturn this decision.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
