OL,3,C'Such little regard for life': Family
OL,4,Ccriticise medics for care failure
OL,6,F"The public support has been fantastic
OL,7,Fand a total gamechanger. As far as
OL,8,FJohn and I are concerned, the court
OL,9,Fand the Jurats are entitled to their
OL,10,Fopinion but we're public servants and
OL,11,Fthe public's opinion matters to us,
OL,12,Ftheir verdict appears to be pretty
OL,13,Funanimous."
OL,15,FHundreds of people gathered outside St
OL,16,FHelier Ambulance Station after the
OL,17,Fguilty verdict to protest the decision.
OL,19,FUnite the Union is calling for a
OL,20,Fjudical review into the legal case.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
