OL,3,C'Such little regard for life': Family
OL,4,Ccriticise medics for care failure
OL,6,FRegional officer James Turner says:
OL,7,F"Unite believes there are serious
OL,8,Fquestions to be asked about how the
OL,9,Flaw has been applied in this case,
OL,10,Fwhether that application was in the
OL,11,Fpublic interest and if the case should
OL,12,Fhave been brought to trial."
OL,14,FA fundraiser set up to support the
OL,15,Fmedics has also raised more than
OL,16,F#47,000, although it has brought their
OL,17,Faccess to legal aid into question.
