OL,3,C'Such little regard for life': Family
OL,4,Ccriticise medics for care failure
OL,6,FLe Sauteur explains: "We are meeting
OL,7,Fthe young lady who set up the
OL,8,Fcrowdfunding page on Wednesday. Both
OL,9,FJohn and I are committed though that,
OL,10,Fno matter what happens, we won't be
OL,11,Ffinancially gaining from this at all.
OL,13,F"We'll have to wait and see where we
OL,14,Fare with funding from legal aid but we
OL,15,Fare committed to appeal and will have
OL,16,Fto do whatever we can to make that
OL,17,Fhappen."
